    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，GradeSync负责成绩同步，它要先查StudentDB的学生信息，然后更新到ClassroomService的课堂数据里。这个流向是GradeSync → StudentDB → ClassroomService。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，CI子图里已经放好这三个组件，连线是B到C再到D。现在生产环境ENV这边，我放了一个LMS_Portal作为子图，里面有个ContentCDN节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
