    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，LMS_Portal是整个生产环境的入口，ContentCDN应该是支撑它的内容分发层。但开发环境的子图名字——你写的是Education_ContentCDN？",
      "elements_involved": [
