      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "其实保持DEV子图叫Education_ContentCDN也可以，虽然里面暂时只有ClassroomService，但开发时ContentCDN和ClassroomService是绑定的。关键是整体流向：开发环境的ClassroomService要能一路走到生产环境的ContentCDN。",
