      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "整体流向是A→B→C→D→E？也就是开发ClassroomService → CI的GradeSync → CI的StudentDB → CI的ClassroomService → 生产的ContentCDN？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
